{"tid":138471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港大正式委任北大學者、人大代表蔡洪濱　掌經濟工管學院","createTime":"2017-02-28T15:19:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T18:43:25.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1225195a2367a8275daaec3b762f1d1c3e2225c5","tid":138471,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:19:09.000Z","msg":"港大校長馬斐森今日向師生發電郵，宣布校委會委任全國人大代表、北京大學光華管理學院前院長蔡洪濱，擔任經濟及工商管理學院院長，今年7月1日正式上任。他將成為首位進入港大的內地大學管理層學者。<br />\n<br />\n港大學苑即時新聞公布了馬斐森的電郵，信中證實校委會在今日開會後決定，委任蔡洪濱作經濟及工商管理學院院長，接替即將卸任的張介教授，任期為5年。馬斐森的電郵讚揚蔡洪濱是一位擁有高度成就的學者，專攻博弈論、中國經濟、工業組織、企業融資等課題，「鑑於他的傑出的資歷，我有信心他將帶領學院到達新水平，並在學術上領導學院超越地區及全球」。<br />\n<br />\n蔡洪濱是內地經濟學者，1997年獲美國史丹福大學經濟學博士及統計學碩士，2010年接替張維迎出任北大光華管理學院院長，直至上月辭職。蔡洪濱亦是全國人大代表（江西省）及北京市政協，曾任多間國企如中石化、聯通的獨立非執董，現時亦擔任一家紐約上市的泰和誠醫療集團獨立非執董。<br />\n <br />\n港大自去年5月啟動遴選程序物色新院長，接替現任院長張介教授，張介是台灣人，由2011年起擔任該職。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/港大正式委任北大學者蔡洪濱-掌經濟工管學院/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E5%8C%97%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85%E8%94%A1%E6%B4%AA%E6%BF%B1-%E6%8E%8C%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%B7%A5%E7%AE%A1%E5%AD%B8%E9%99%A2%2F&d=HYT0XJgSPTYEb9NwUTCrmnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=e75912ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E5%8C%97%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85%E8%94%A1%E6%B4%AA%E6%BF%B1-%E6%8E%8C%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%B7%A5%E7%AE%A1%E5%AD%B8%E9%99%A2%2F&h=b762c0b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/港大正式委任北大學者蔡洪濱-掌經濟工管學院/</a>"},{"pid":"967f183968ab5bd22f56799eede2c3b75a0c0c4d","tid":138471,"uid":42435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:21:29.000Z","msg":"香港大學改名＂特區人民大學＂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59163c7e349b0eaa7c92b502c84cfeb4f808c39c","tid":138471,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:27:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港大學改名＂特區人民大學＂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nXGU <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78f6ae36ce0138b8637a46092ab2d4676dd68174","tid":138471,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:28:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fc003acc0eef9f39ca42c0384a3635046709a2b","tid":138471,"uid":32473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:30:34.000Z","msg":"佢係大陸間大學辭職理由係話要睇住個女 家庭理由<br />\n睇來做左港大院長 家庭問題就可以解決<br />\n支那人就算學識幾高都係咁樣鐘意講大話"},{"pid":"d1b253176fb3cbc79e6256b8bb5ae73ec7d40190","tid":138471,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:36:47.000Z","msg":"當年張五常搞起既港大經濟系俾條北佬揸旗，睇怕可以收皮"},{"pid":"8e7458cfa532c3706127bfbbc7c69fe61ae0f6b8","tid":138471,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:37:57.000Z","msg":"Xianggang University<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b6ff9e179c72ed965f8d41abe0817fdfccf992","tid":138471,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:45:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年張五常搞起既港大經濟系俾條北佬揸旗，睇怕可以收皮</blockquote><br />\n張五常都潛逃左去深圳啦"},{"pid":"601b8f03a97c7d04d23cdabc7794feb361ab6cfe","tid":138471,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:54:32.000Z","msg":"真係悲哀，由張五常去到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307b62f1036e0a97aabf4a6be9464d57604c4149","tid":138471,"uid":6959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:56:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66e9b132aee9cee984f62af1fa2c1fb5fffd69bf","tid":138471,"uid":83052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:59:23.000Z","msg":"其實睇CV都幾勁，只要物色程序無bias其實無咩問題"},{"pid":"9e36bd7f1f7e294bf96a9b7d515c9c66da28fea1","tid":138471,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:07:11.000Z","msg":"hku真係比班蝗搞死"},{"pid":"922b577bc1abb0d899a74544508e14a6abcfeab7","tid":138471,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:08:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實睇CV都幾勁，只要物色程序無bias其實無咩問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中大之前揾劉遵義做校長，又係standford econ <br />\n結果係咁斬樹又奶共<br />\n<br />\n大專揾左仔揸旗都係奶野多"},{"pid":"8af7059747ad5c16e134670975ffc9f116db5365","tid":138471,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:27:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實睇CV都幾勁，只要物色程序無bias其實無咩問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中大之前揾劉遵義做校長，又係standford econ <br />\n結果係咁斬樹又奶共<br />\n<br />\n大專揾左仔揸旗都係奶野多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前中大真係用中文教書，後來劉遵義大執CU教學語言，全部強制轉做英文。<br />\n<br />\n當時好多中大學生反佢，話有損中大傳統。其實而家睇番，改做英文教學不失為明舉。"},{"pid":"fca44f37dccd5fdba4a31fb5c3b5eb8c98b199ca","tid":138471,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:29:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實睇CV都幾勁，只要物色程序無bias其實無咩問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中大之前揾劉遵義做校長，又係standford econ <br />\n結果係咁斬樹又奶共<br />\n<br />\n大專揾左仔揸旗都係奶野多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前中大真係用中文教書，後來劉遵義大執CU教學語言，全部強制轉做英文。<br />\n<br />\n當時好多中大學生反佢，話有損中大傳統。其實而家睇番，改做英文教學不失為明舉。</blockquote><br />\n中文教書食得屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ae2d3cecc093b0c388e79826e3748f37f8d18d","tid":138471,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:42:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實睇CV都幾勁，只要物色程序無bias其實無咩問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中大之前揾劉遵義做校長，又係standford econ <br />\n結果係咁斬樹又奶共<br />\n<br />\n大專揾左仔揸旗都係奶野多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前中大真係用中文教書，後來劉遵義大執CU教學語言，全部強制轉做英文。<br />\n<br />\n當時好多中大學生反佢，話有損中大傳統。其實而家睇番，改做英文教學不失為明舉。</blockquote><br />\n中文教書食得屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCU用中文教學既背景，係因為當年殖民地管治下，中文地位岌岌可危，一班學人為左保存中文傳統所以先提倡中文教學。<br />\n<br />\n而家睇返件事，如果仲死守呢個傳統，呢間U真係同國際完全脫軌。唔係話佢教學質素下降，而係做唔到好typical既國際化研究形/綜合形大學，最多只能成為嶺大呢種好localised、regional的，以人文精神作招徠既liberal 學院"},{"pid":"e9a9099efb3df47cf4a7b85902aa7f3eee6f4edb","tid":138471,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T17:09:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係悲哀，由張五常去到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要個新人專攻佢最憎既game theory<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7cb9c4f677ed792d93c79cf7ab65ca711d36243","tid":138471,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T17:09:33.000Z","msg":"Btw六常點睇"},{"pid":"c37bd8c56aef2aae18373cec293f97ec77b225c0","tid":138471,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T17:10:59.000Z","msg":"港大人: 要打卡 show off ABC 不了"},{"pid":"23b1effb14f1cb7265403ff315276b0d4a1732c9","tid":138471,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T17:30:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真係悲哀，由張五常去到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要個新人專攻佢最憎既game theory<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n史德拉曾經對人說：「當世少運用數學的經濟學者祇有三人：艾智仁、高斯、<span style=\"color: red;\">張五常</span>。」"},{"pid":"f3015b17807522e13338633043725edac56eb223","tid":138471,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T17:51:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實睇CV都幾勁，只要物色程序無bias其實無咩問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中大之前揾劉遵義做校長，又係standford econ <br />\n結果係咁斬樹又奶共<br />\n<br />\n大專揾左仔揸旗都係奶野多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前中大真係用中文教書，後來劉遵義大執CU教學語言，全部強制轉做英文。<br />\n<br />\n當時好多中大學生反佢，話有損中大傳統。其實而家睇番，改做英文教學不失為明舉。</blockquote><br />\n中文教書食得屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCU用中文教學既背景，係因為當年殖民地管治下，中文地位岌岌可危，一班學人為左保存中文傳統所以先提倡中文教學。<br />\n<br />\n而家睇返件事，如果仲死守呢個傳統，呢間U真係同國際完全脫軌。唔係話佢教學質素下降，而係做唔到好typical既國際化研究形/綜合形大學，最多只能成為嶺大呢種好localised、regional的，以人文精神作招徠既liberal 學院</blockquote><br />\n咁你東大夠用日文，ETH都係用番德文<br />\n成日話建國，但連自己語文文化都蔑視，何其諷刺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 我覺得間學校有好既基礎同實力，一定有人欣賞，好過搞埋堆19表面野"},{"pid":"ab44aff42bc35a614852bc46688be640ad674206","tid":138471,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T17:55:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實睇CV都幾勁，只要物色程序無bias其實無咩問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中大之前揾劉遵義做校長，又係standford econ <br />\n結果係咁斬樹又奶共<br />\n<br />\n大專揾左仔揸旗都係奶野多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前中大真係用中文教書，後來劉遵義大執CU教學語言，全部強制轉做英文。<br />\n<br />\n當時好多中大學生反佢，話有損中大傳統。其實而家睇番，改做英文教學不失為明舉。</blockquote><br />\n中文教書食得屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCU用中文教學既背景，係因為當年殖民地管治下，中文地位岌岌可危，一班學人為左保存中文傳統所以先提倡中文教學。<br />\n<br />\n而家睇返件事，如果仲死守呢個傳統，呢間U真係同國際完全脫軌。唔係話佢教學質素下降，而係做唔到好typical既國際化研究形/綜合形大學，最多只能成為嶺大呢種好localised、regional的，以人文精神作招徠既liberal 學院</blockquote><br />\n咁你東大夠用日文，ETH都係用番德文<br />\n成日話建國，但連自己語文文化都蔑視，何其諷刺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 我覺得間學校有好既基礎同實力，一定有人欣賞，好過搞埋堆19表面野</blockquote><br />\n香港咩定位呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小城市靠國際化高等學府唔用英文唔通圍爐取暖咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a09e43a27949bd51892db3d639ab99084810d9d0","tid":138471,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T17:58:54.000Z","msg":"港大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f90473c028748b5f6f53eaab56715436c6f55d","tid":138471,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T17:59:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當初仲笑人中大，依家呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb70726732b3538e0e35b78e308c66eac29662b","tid":138471,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T18:12:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實睇CV都幾勁，只要物色程序無bias其實無咩問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中大之前揾劉遵義做校長，又係standford econ <br />\n結果係咁斬樹又奶共<br />\n<br />\n大專揾左仔揸旗都係奶野多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前中大真係用中文教書，後來劉遵義大執CU教學語言，全部強制轉做英文。<br />\n<br />\n當時好多中大學生反佢，話有損中大傳統。其實而家睇番，改做英文教學不失為明舉。</blockquote><br />\n中文教書食得屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCU用中文教學既背景，係因為當年殖民地管治下，中文地位岌岌可危，一班學人為左保存中文傳統所以先提倡中文教學。<br />\n<br />\n而家睇返件事，如果仲死守呢個傳統，呢間U真係同國際完全脫軌。唔係話佢教學質素下降，而係做唔到好typical既國際化研究形/綜合形大學，最多只能成為嶺大呢種好localised、regional的，以人文精神作招徠既liberal 學院</blockquote><br />\n咁你東大夠用日文，ETH都係用番德文<br />\n成日話建國，但連自己語文文化都蔑視，何其諷刺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 我覺得間學校有好既基礎同實力，一定有人欣賞，好過搞埋堆19表面野</blockquote><br 